.\" Manpage for shutdowntimer

.TH man 1 "06 Sep 2017" "3.0" "shutdowntimer man page"
.SH NAME
shutdowntimer \- Shuts down your computer after a timeout
.SH SYNOPSIS
shutdowntimer
.SH DESCRIPTION
shutdowntimer uses Zenity to display progress bar. Zenity is used for notifications in Ubuntu, Xubuntu and possibly other distros.
Unless you close the notification window before the countdown ends, the computer shuts down. At script start it uses mpg123 to 
play $HOME/.shutdowntimer/sound.mp3
Feel free to edit the script or change the mp3 file to your needs.
.SH AUTHOR
